# Next.js Frontend Patterns

- **Server Components** default — fetching data, layout, static content
- **Client Components** ('use client') — interaktivitas, hooks, state, event handlers
- **React Query** — server state (useQuery, useMutation)
- **Zustand** — client state (filter, UI state)
- **Zod** — form validation (lib/validators.ts)
- **Tailwind CSS** — utility-first styling
